duties_responsibilities.duty: Design, develop, configure, test, and document applications and integrations based on project specifications.
Lead solution delivery and implementation for programs and projects.
Troubleshoot and resolve performance issues in server components, DB components, and UI.
Ensure user stories are developer-ready, easy to understand, and testable.
Write custom code or scripts for testing to ensure resiliency in production.
Adhere to maintenance plans, project timelines, and support plan summaries.
Participate in learning activities around modern software design and development core practices.
Keep abreast of current technologies and technological trends.
Review and discuss code from more senior engineers to understand best practices and design patterns.
Provide technical leadership in multiple phases of a project and ensure coordination of assignments.
Utilize agile project management tools and concepts to ensure projects are delivered on time and on budget.
Maintain knowledge of development methods, best practices, and standards.
Work closely with IT Security to ensure all systems follow industry standards and policies.

education_certification.credential: Bachelor’s degree in information services or related field (Master's preferred)
